{
  "id": "63f607b6dfb5be001cc2c093",
  "title": "未来を予測する最良の方法は、それを発明することだ",
  "created": 1677068216,
  "updated": 1677068829,
  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "63f607b6dfb5be001cc2c093",
      "text": "未来を予測する最良の方法は、それを発明することだ",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1677068216,
      "updated": 1677068216
    },
    {
      "id": "63f609d0aff09e0000b679e8",
      "text": ">“Don’t worry about what anybody else is going to do… The best way to predict the future is to invent it. Really smart people with reasonable funding can do just about anything that doesn’t violate too many of Newton’s Laws!”",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1677068752,
      "updated": 1677068754
    },
    {
      "id": "63f607b8aff09e0000204fba",
      "text": "\t[Alan Kay] (1971) at a 1971 meeting of [PARC]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1677068216,
      "updated": 1677068752
    },
    {
      "id": "63f607bfaff09e0000204fbe",
      "text": "\tref: https://quoteinvestigator.com/2012/09/27/invent-the-future/?amp=1",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1677068225,
      "updated": 1677068784
    },
    {
      "id": "63f609f0aff09e0000b679e9",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1677068785,
      "updated": 1677068785
    },
    {
      "id": "63f60939aff09e0000b679e5",
      "text": "関連",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1677068602,
      "updated": 1677068607
    },
    {
      "id": "63f6093eaff09e0000b679e6",
      "text": "\t1963年、Gábor Dénesが[未来は予測できないが、未来は発明できる]と書いた。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1677068607,
      "updated": 1677068809
    },
    {
      "id": "63f60a10aff09e0000b679ea",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1677068816,
      "updated": 1677068816
    },
    {
      "id": "63f607c0aff09e0000204fc2",
      "text": ">[https://twitter.com/nishio/status/1628317176099901442?s=20 @nishio]: 「未来を予測する最良の方法はそれを創ることだ」的なニュアンスの言葉、エンジニアは「アランケイだね」と思う人がほとんどだと思うが、実は世の中には「ドラッカーだね」派もいるらしくて、どっちが正しいのか気になってる",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1677068225,
      "updated": 1677068237
    },
    {
      "id": "63f607ccaff09e0000204fc4",
      "text": ">[https://twitter.com/nishio/status/1628347564490899456?s=20 @nishio]: [https://quoteinvestigator.com/2012/09/27/invent-the-future/?amp=1 We Cannot Predict the Future, But We Can Invent It – Quote Investigator®]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1677068237,
      "updated": 1677068266
    },
    {
      "id": "63f607d5aff09e0000204fc5",
      "text": ">ドラッカーだと言われ出したのは1986。アランケイがthe best way to predict the future is to invent itと言ったのは1983。少し違う表現ではガーボルデーネシュが1963年にやってる。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1677068245,
      "updated": 1677068245
    },
    {
      "id": "63f607d5aff09e0000204fc6",
      "text": ">[https://twitter.com/nishio/status/1628347827276648449?s=20 @nishio]: ガーボルデーネシュやアランケイと言われてピンとこない人が適当にドラッカーだと言い出したのだろうな。",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1677068245,
      "updated": 1677068283
    },
    {
      "id": "63f607c0aff09e0000204fc3",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1677068225,
      "updated": 1677068225
    },
    {
      "id": "63f607b8aff09e0000204fbc",
      "text": "[未来予測] [発明]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
